channel.title: Chaging the Ip of the Open source client of DDSSPECED, i tried everything
channel.description:
How do i change the Ip, i went in the client.java, it didnt work. I was told other stuff, and i can't seem to figure it out, any one experienced in this? If so, please share your knowledge :P
O and my Client complier, says it can't find a path, when i try to complie, maby that is a problem? I did change the Ip in the client.java to mine, but i tried to complie, and it didnt work.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: November 12, 2008, 07:54:38 pm[/size][hr]Anyone know :([br][br][size=1]Posted on: November 12, 2008, 07:55:12 pm[/size][hr]I'll keep checking, i am really hoping someone knows this :(

item.dc:creator: @klomp3 klomp3
item.description:
@klomp3 wrote:

go in client folders to EGUI.
U will see like “localhost”, “localhost”, “localhost”
Change that to the ip u want and its done, compile and restart.

Greetz,
Klomp3
